Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:16.96,Default Above,,0,0,0,,Wah, cucuku yang senang imut banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.92,tanda,,0,0,0,,(Pyar)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:34.76,Default Above,,0,0,0,,Wah!
